### Configuration
@host = http://localhost:8080
@ingId = ing1

### f) Tester la récupération des mouvements (GET)
GET {{host}}/ingredients/{{ingId}}/stockMovements?from=2026-03-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-03-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### g) Tester l'ajout de mouvements (POST)
POST {{host}}/ingredients/{{ingId}}/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "unit": "KG",
    "value": 12.5,
    "type": "entrée"
  },
  {
    "unit": "L",
    "value": 2.0,
    "type": "sortie"
  },
  {
    "unit": "PCS",
    "value": 50.0,
    "type": "entrée"
  }
]

###

### Tester l'erreur 404 - Ingrédient inexistant (GET)
# Doit retourner 404 et "Ingredient.id=999 is not found" [cite: 18]
GET {{host}}/ingredients/999/stockMovements?from=2026-03-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-03-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### Tester l'erreur 404 - Ingrédient inexistant (POST)
# Doit retourner 404 et "Ingredient.id=non-existant is not found" [cite: 23]
POST {{host}}/ingredients/non-existant/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "unit": "PCS",
    "value": 1.0,
    "type": "sortie"
  }
]